title: Star Wars' trailer to air on - Monday Night Football' - Detroit News
text:
'Star Wars' trailer to air on 'Monday Night Football' LOS ANGELES - More than just football fans will likely be tuning in to watch halftime on "Monday Night Football" this week. Check out this story on detroitnews.com: http://detne.ws/1RQD1kG The latest official Star Wars poster was recently released.
 Detroit News.
